              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Details" typeId="fa11-60d9-4bb8-7538">Increasse this Formation Commander&apos;s Command Leadership distance from 6&quot;/15cm to 8&quot;/20cm.
Discard this card: Automatically pass one Unit Last Stand Test for a Unit from this Formation whose Unit Leader is within 8&quot;/20cm of the Formation Commander.</characteristic>
